00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:05,000
anong ginagawa mo

518
00:39:07,280 --> 00:39:08,560
Sa aking libro,

519
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:10,560
walang pagsuko sa kalahati.

520
00:39:18,280 --> 00:39:19,360
Bakit ka bumangon?

521
00:39:20,360 --> 00:39:21,616
Uuwi ako para
magpagaling ng ilang araw.

522
00:39:21,640 --> 00:39:22,616
Hindi.

523
00:39:22,640 --> 00:39:23,640
May lagnat ka pa.

524
00:39:23,960 --> 00:39:25,160
Isa itong sikolohikal na isyu.

525
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:27,200
Hindi ito mapapagaling sa pamamagitan ng
mga iniksyon o gamot.

526
00:39:27,880 --> 00:39:29,600
Aasa lang ako sa strong will ko para lumaban.

527
00:39:30,160 --> 00:39:31,416
Ibibili kita ng gamot.

528
00:39:31,440 --> 00:39:32,440
Hindi na kailangan.

529
00:39:33,720 --> 00:39:34,720
nga pala,

530
00:39:35,160 --> 00:39:36,376
Ayokong makita si Chi Cheng,

531
00:39:36,400 --> 00:39:37,680
pansamantala.

532
00:39:38,280 --> 00:39:39,400
Kung pupunta siya para makita ako,

533
00:39:39,480 --> 00:39:40,480
deal with him for me.

534
00:39:41,080 --> 00:39:42,056
Okay.

535
00:39:42,080 --> 00:39:43,080
salamat po.

536
00:39:46,280 --> 00:39:47,280
Kabutihan.

537
00:39:47,640 --> 00:39:48,616
Da Wei.

538
00:39:48,640 --> 00:39:49,640
Iyong tsinelas.

539
00:40:01,880 --> 00:40:03,520
Hindi ko alam kung may gusto ba ako sa mga lalaki o hindi.

540
00:40:03,880 --> 00:40:04,920
Pero alam ko

541
00:40:05,840 --> 00:40:06,840
na ako

542
00:40:07,200 --> 00:40:08,240
gusto kita.

543
00:40:21,800 --> 00:40:23,016
(Da Bao: Huling online ilang araw na ang nakalipas)

544
00:40:23,040 --> 00:40:24,160
(Kaway)

545
00:40:31,160 --> 00:40:33,720
(Leather Bag)

546
00:40:44,400 --> 00:40:45,400
Darn it.

547
00:41:03,640 --> 00:41:04,640
nasaan siya?

548
00:41:04,880 --> 00:41:05,880
Nag-trip siya.

549
00:41:17,120 --> 00:41:18,097
Kung kukunin mo iyon,

550
00:41:18,121 --> 00:41:19,656
magagalit siya sayo pagbalik niya.

551
00:41:19,680 --> 00:41:20,680
Kung galit siya sa akin,

552
00:41:21,320 --> 00:41:22,480
darating siya para hanapin ako.

553
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:27,200
(Bonus Clip)

554
00:41:35,720 --> 00:41:36,840
Nandito ka ba para kay Wu Suo Wei?

555
00:41:38,560 --> 00:41:39,560
Nasa back room siya.
